# Connect-you-and-me-connect-the-world-2023

作品《连接你我、连通世界》荣获第十四届蓝桥杯全国软件和信息技术专业人才大赛-视觉艺术设计赛全国总决赛视频设计类三等奖。
His work "Connecting you and me, Connecting the World" won the third prize in the video design category of the 14th Blue Bridge Cup National Software and Information Technology Professionals Competition - Visual Art Design Competition National Finals.

